{"tid":1798581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地唔好再撚狗","createTime":"2019-12-26T10:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T11:59:48.000Z","uid":151587,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"40cc19b8e42f6cfda3532540059ddfbdaff51ae5","tid":1798581,"uid":151587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:19:33.000Z","msg":"發夢經過moko<br />\n明明全部人圍喺中庭睇住班曱甴同手足捉依因<br />\n班曱甴根本豪無頭緒自己想做咩<br />\n之後有一隊曱甴行過<br />\n有手足忍唔住撚左兩句<br />\n就引左50+曱甴過後黎<br />\n最少十幾個手足比曱甴查證<br />\n雖然叫無咩捐失<br />\n但真係好無謂<br />\n要記住撚狗唔會令佢地少左忽肉<br />\n只會激化曱甴對手足怨恨<br />\n打手足打得更落力<br />\n真係求下唔好再撚狗"},{"pid":"be6e03162ca721202afe6bca6b03d35baf9ae87d","tid":1798581,"uid":263618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:21:55.000Z","msg":"agree <br />\n平時搭地鐵你見到精神病人你都行去另一個車廂啦,而家呢啲人比精神病人更加癲,出嚟抗爭唔係為咗發洩啊"},{"pid":"8d94075dba6dbc107f4e8d2ea569c38f5c9a2299","tid":1798581,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"商場又細又窄咪撚"},{"pid":"605a8a6e6729845dfad44bd66923604a2fd677bc","tid":1798581,"uid":151587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be6e03162ca721202afe6bca6b03d35baf9ae87d","tid":1798581,"uid":263618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:21:55.000Z","msg":"agree <br />\n平時搭地鐵你見到精神病人你都行去另一個車廂啦,而家呢啲人比精神病人更加癲,出嚟抗爭唔係為咗發洩啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"好同意你嗰句<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出黎抗爭唔係為左發洩</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c9e285515ee95172109efa0b16b84b8c155d5a27","tid":1798581,"uid":10521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:44:23.000Z","msg":"一有人提就有人衝出嚟話：「咁撚狗/著黑衫/帶頭盔...係咪犯法先？你唔做就代表你屈服，留喺屋企唔好出啦屌你！」<br />\n依家打仗啊dllm！為啖氣去撚狗最後俾人捉，邊個損失多啲？一方面屌啲狗殺人唔眨眼，另一方面引狗捉你，又話煲底見？勇者不懼，但都唔好送頭，或者累死走唔甩嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8ec60b953050116b9bd2d014391d9720c9760b","tid":1798581,"uid":188685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">12.29 愛丁堡<br />\n12.31 和你拖<br />\n1.1 兩點維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">*請準時 勿打尖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中環pepe專門店=人血饅頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sEDqHed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsEDqHed.jpg&h=a0e32cbc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5ac6FU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5ac6FU.jpg&h=3c3c596d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mBY98Uf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmBY98Uf.jpg&h=14d81587&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Jzxnef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Jzxnef.jpg&h=59b52e16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51sZMFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51sZMFV.jpg&h=3c6470d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/26/183356_db27ee0c31f4e189305863ccc0f061a4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F26%2F183356_db27ee0c31f4e189305863ccc0f061a4.jpeg&h=e7591aa0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e54a2c5d077a91a9a027bf8d9890fec882de16bb","tid":1798581,"uid":113222,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"A地點有手足屌狗，狗去A地點查身分證搞事，但如果A地點手足無屌狗，班狗會點？<br />\n<br />\n答案係去左B地點或者C地點搞事。<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩撚狗會令佢地更敵視示威者，事實係佢地一早已經當左示威者係敵人，死左咁多人，開左咁多次真槍，你仲對佢地心存希望係不切實際。"},{"pid":"c8b096c5cddb637668a43115381dcfaea9be02c4","tid":1798581,"uid":84176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家唔好再喺警曱收隊時屌佢地啦<br />\n我地今日目標係要令商場閂門呀"},{"pid":"aed870a5ab281dd917e66c9434492219eface